comments.body:
[~jlowe], great work! It looks good to me overall including error handling and resource management.

Minor nits:

How about adding helper methods like getKeyPrefix/getNodePath for getting key prefix and node path? ZKRMStateStore also does so.
{code}
    String keyPrefix = RM_APP_ROOT + "/" + appId + "/";
    ...
    String appKey = RM_APP_ROOT + "/" + appId
{code}

I found that the patch includes lots hard-coded "/".  I think it's better to have private field SEPARATOR = "/".

